'''Rula''' was a [[Smuggler/Legends|smuggler]] [[Captain/Legends|captain]] in command of a fleet of twenty [[Starship/Legends|ships]]. Prior to the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]], [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]] had smuggled guns with Rula's fleet. They had attempted to hide from the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] on the edge of the [[Hapes Cluster/Legends|Hapes Cluster]]. However, a single [[Hapan Battle Dragon]] discovered them and destroyed all but three of Rula's ships. The event left Han Solo with a long-lasting distrust of [[Hapan]]s.

